title: Fox News hosts accuse liberal media of 'racial' attacks against Ben Carson
text: The right media has been prevalent in their attacks against President Obama over the last seven years. Often criticized for their attacks having racial undertones, the leading conservative news outlet is turning the tables on their liberal counterparts. youtube.com
